# Asterisks may only be used at the end of a string, and allow a word to continue.
# :: with surrounding spaces separates human language (left) from pony language (right).
# A line may start with a hash to make the line a comment.
# Lower case allows any case, the last characters case select the case on any character afterward.
# Spaces (excluding no breaking spaces) is wildcard for any non-alphanumerical character.

